Titolo: Hysteria Project

Anno: 2009

Descrizione: Hysteria Project is a 2009 FMV survival horror adventure game developed and published by French studio BulkyPix for iOS and  first released on the App Store on April 7, 2009. It was released as a PlayStation mini available for play on the PlayStation 3 and PlayStation Portable on April 15, 2010 in Europe and April 22, 2010 in North America. The port was published by Sanuk Games. A sequel was released on the App Store in 2011, Hysteria Project 2.